              <title>Evaluating conferences</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/2572</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/2572</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>An important component of any conference is getting feedback from participants so you can improve the experience both during the conference and the next time you plan one.&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li>What questions do you ask and when? </li>
<li>What are the best methods for gathering feedback from conference participants?&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
<li>What are some useful tools?</li>
<li>How do you manage the data and share the results?</li>
</ul><p>Contact details: Sylvia Currie, scurrie@bccampus.ca</p>]]></description>
