                    <item>
              <title>Publishing resources, photos, and other materials</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/2571</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/2571</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>There are many questions to consider around publishing resources, photos, and other materials that are generated through conference participation. For example:</p>
<ul>
<li>How do conference organizers manage accounts and permissions to publish materials?</li>
<li>How do you handle permissions to publish photographs taken at conferences?</li>
<li>How do you encourage participants to share? </li>
<li>What do conference delegates need to know in advance?&nbsp;</li>
<li>What online services are available to facilitate publishing and sharing?</li>
</ul>
<p>What are your questions and suggestions?</p><p>Contact details: Sylvia Currie, scurrie@bccampus.ca</p>]]></description>
